## Description {#details}

Typed, array-like tuple of metadata.

This is a wrapper for <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdtuple">MDTuple</a></em> that makes it act like an array holding a particular type of metadata.

Definition at line 1635 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/metadata-h">Metadata.h</a>.
